data.description: Welcome to your dream waterfront oasis in Cocoa Beach, Florida! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is perfectly situated on a serene canal, offering you a slice of coastal paradise. Spanning 2600 square feet of luxurious living space, this residence boasts both style and functionality. As you step through the grand entrance, you are greeted by the elegance of high ceilings and an abundance of natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The first floor hosts a spacious primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat for ultimate comfort and convenience. Ascend the staircase to the second floor, where three charming bedrooms await, all adorned with beautiful wood flooring. Take in the breathtaking views from not one, but two balconies, ideal for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying the vibrant Florida sunsets. Step into the backyard, a true haven for relaxation and entertainment. Marvel at the panoramic canal views!
